<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 8 (Xinhua) -- People from Hong Kong's
industrial and commercial circles will hold a grand evening party
on September 30 to celebrate the 48th National Day of the People's
Republic of China.
</P>
<P>
Some 200 industrial and business leaders of the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region (SAR) met today to discuss the
forming of the preparatory committee for the celebration.
</P>
<P>
