meeting that Hong Kong has maintained its economic prosperity and
social stability after its return to the motherland. This is the
result of the central government's efforts in implementing "one
country, two systems" policy, and the result of the concerted
efforts by the HKSAR government and the whole of Hong Kong people.
</P>
<P>
