of the motherland are a major factor supporting Hong Kong's
stability and prosperity. Now Hong Kong has returned to the
motherland, both Hong Kong and the interior areas will benefit
from the increasingly frequent economic and trade exchanges.
</P>
<P>
This year's National Day celebration bears special meaning and
everybody should feel excited at the first National Day after the
birth of the SAR, he said.  
