we are going to win again and go for seven," he said.
</P>
<P>
The NBA superstar has long helped sell Nike's lucrative Air
Jordan line. The brand will continue to feature the Jumpman
logo. The new line is set to appear in November.
</P>
<P>
The most expensive shoe sold by the new Nike division will be
the dlrs 150 Air Jordan. Jordan recently signed a dlrs 33 million,
one-year contract that makes him the highest-paid player in
basketball. 
