Ismail shot into the back of the net from a free kick.
</P>
<P>
In the 83rd minute Mohamed Nizam scored the equalizer with a
30-yard left foot kick which landed straight in the net.
</P>
<P>
India has four points in the tournament, Pakistan and Sri Lanka
three, the Maldives two, Bangladesh one and Nepal zero.
</P>
<P>
Sri Lanka and Maldives meet Wednesday for the first semi-finals
while India and Pakistan face off Thursday in the second
semi-finals. 
