<P>
The matches in six different groups will be hosted in six
Nigerian cities -- Lagos, Kaduna, Kano, Enugu, Calabar and
Ibadan. The proposal listed Bauchi and Ilorin as two alternative
venues.
</P>
<P>
A total of 24 teams will compete in the championships, the
biggest ever in the event's history.
</P>
<P>
</P>
