building socialism with Chinese characteristics, and under the
leadership of the Party Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at the
core, take further efforts to build up the Party style and a clean
government, and intensify the fight against corruption, so as to
make new contributions for the realization of the strategic plan
to be set forth at the forthcoming 15th National Congress of the
the 15th National Congress of the CPC, the communique says. 
