<DOCNO> XIE19970909.0260 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-09 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 12 Dead in Norway Chopper Crash </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, September 8 (Xinhua) -- All 12 people aboard a
helicopter were feared to be dead after the plane crashed today in
the northern coastal area of Norway.
</P>
<P>
Two bodies were recovered hours after the crash and rescuers
found some wreckage of the plane.
</P>
<P>
The helicopter disappeared from the radar 10 minutes before its
scheduled landing on a platform in Nornefaeltet, an oil field in
the Norwegian Sea. It took off from the northern town of
Broennoeysund around 06:00 a.m. local time (0500 GMT). 
</P>
</TEXT>
