<HEADLINE> Otis Forms Holding Company in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Otis Elevator of the United
States today announced formation of Otis China Limited, a joint
venture holding company in which it will have majority share, it
said in a press statement from Connecticut, where it is based.
</P>
<P>
Since 1984, Otis has set up joint ventures in Tianjin, Beijing,
Shanghai, Guangzhou and Hangzhou and has built a network of more
than 100 branch offices throughout the country.
</P>
<P>
The formation of Otis China, which will manage Otis' five
operations in the country, "is a natural result of the successful
evolution of our business partnerships in China", Pier Luigi
Foschi, executive vice president for Pacific Asia was quoted as
saying.
</P>
<P>
Otis Elevator, a subsidiary of United Technologies Corporation,
is the world's leading company in the manufacture and service of
people-moving equipment, including elevators, escalators, moving
walkways and shuttle systems. 
